{"tid":2259570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無30歲既人諗緊自己5-60歲會點?","createTime":"2020-10-27T02:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T15:53:01.000Z","uid":196751,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e1484365a3d4d93f630a59f64bc37eca0cd52b3f","tid":2259570,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"自己本身做緊果行唔錯<br />\n但係又見過同行50歲比人炒<br />\n炒左出去搵唔返呢個水平要轉做低收入人士<br />\n<br />\n加上香港咁既情況<br />\n每日出街都見好多廢老<br />\n又窮又要為口又要為醫療諗<br />\n<br />\n當然你話儲錢,投資做多d被動收入<br />\n但始終唔係一個好穩定既方法<br />\n大家都係散戶,好多時都係被操縱多<br />\n<br />\n我同輩好多人做狗<br />\n鐵飯碗又有得出黎蝦蝦霸霸<br />\n不過我唔羨慕<br />\n寧願為生活煩惱都唔想做一個人渣"},{"pid":"b0b022b1a9fcbeb44ba65f75109cb3dc4007252f","tid":2259570,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:44:10.000Z","msg":"未供完樓<br />\n<br />\n希望樓升左一倍<br />\n工資跟通漲升，比人炒左，做secure 都夠供樓。"},{"pid":"7b322ca6e056cb3f95b49e75c25c90ff5fc612d5","tid":2259570,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時都唔知點算"},{"pid":"64da80b351f6b47dbc54c52b369ef5916a49e23c","tid":2259570,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b022b1a9fcbeb44ba65f75109cb3dc4007252f","tid":2259570,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:44:10.000Z","msg":"未供完樓<br />\n<br />\n希望樓升左一倍<br />\n工資跟通漲升，比人炒左，做secure 都夠供樓。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"樓升左70%<br />\n<br />\n人工今年無得升,但長遠都差唔多到頂<br />\n每個月都好多開支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5fd5873728033fff01141efc91c45d3f7eafd5","tid":2259570,"uid":190705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"諗黎都冇用 廢事晒精神諗<br />\n睇到個垃圾政府 就知諗黎冇用"},{"pid":"6f342d7124d29c436fcceb187aeec51cea36c6df","tid":2259570,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b322ca6e056cb3f95b49e75c25c9